    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a dream on the road. I\u2019ve spent many weekends keeping her running smooth and looking sharp. While she\u2019s got a tiny bit of 'personality' from years of fun adventures, she still turns heads at every stoplight and drives like a champ. I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate her as much as I have. Come on over, let's chat cars, and take her for a spin\u2014you won't regret it!",
