    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This platform is a masterclass in mechanical synergy, featuring a powertrain that\u2019s been meticulously sorted for peak volumetric efficiency. The engine exhibits rock-solid compression across the board, delivering a linear torque curve that rewards aggressive throttle modulation. I\u2019ve ensured the drivetrain remains taut, with zero lash in the differential and crisp engagement through every gear. Suspension geometry is optimized for neutral turn-in, while the cooling system\u2019s thermal capacity has been verified for sustained high-load cycles. This isn't just a driver; it\u2019s a precision instrument with a chassis that communicates every nuance of the tarmac. Mechanically robust and aesthetically sharp, it\u2019s ready for the most demanding enthusiast.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
