    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you crest a coastal ridge, the rhythmic hum of this classic engine singing a duet with the crashing waves. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time machine crafted for those who prefer the winding road to the straight line. Every gentle crease in the leather tells a story of a sun-drenched weekend getaway, and the gleaming silhouette reflects a legacy of style that modern vehicles simply cannot replicate. It possesses that rare, soulful character that makes every trip feel like a grand event. It has been lived in, it has been loved, and it is ready to be the protagonist in your next great chapter.",
      "price": 38500.0,
