      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to look at my pride and joy. Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see her go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy that smooth engine and classic feel. She\u2019s been incredibly reliable for me\u2014always starts right up and handles like a dream on those weekend drives. I\u2019ve kept her well-maintained and clean, though you might find a tiny scratch here or there that just shows she\u2019s been loved and driven. If you're looking for a dependable ride that still turns heads, this is the one. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
